DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T1.CurveId, T1.SeqSegment, T1.Seq, T2.Quote Quote FROM ORE.dbo.CurveConfigurationQuotes T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.MdatMarketDataDefinitions T2 ON T1.Quote = T2.Quote ORDER BY 1 ASC, 2 ASC, 3 ASC

field.name: *Quote
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.Quote, Quote Lookup FROM ORE.dbo.MdatMarketDataDefinitions !T! ORDER BY !T!.Quote
